         The actual value = The receive data/100.
         The unit of actual value is volt.
         "
    ::= { acdcRectifierInfoEntry 6 }
    
    rectifierInputVoltageUab OBJECT-TYPE
    SYNTAX INTEGER
    MAX-ACCESS read-only
    STATUS current
    DESCRIPTION "
